tweet: Congrats to the MSU Spartans!  #finalfour. Unbelievable coaching by Tom Izzo, and all the Spartan players stepped up and played BIG in the biggest game of the year! Fun game to be at with my dad, @Mateen_Cleaves, @Bmosallam63, and so many other amazing Spartans!  https://t.co/0UMPrIoa4o
